overview: Despite the cold, hunger and harsh environment of a reality TV show, Jackson and Cadence thrive on their intense sexual chemistry. Back in the real world, Cadence tries to rekindle their steamy adventures. Trouble is, she has a boyfriend and Jackson shares a gorgeous girlfriend with his roommate. Will Cadence pursue Jackson or stay with Donnie? Get NAKED and find out!
tagline: Most Primal Passion On Reality TV
title: Naked
